snippet.title: F1® 2019 | ‘Legends Edition: Senna and Prost’ | Reveal Trailer [US]
snippet.description:
Are you ready for the greatest ever F1® rivalry? Introducing the Legends Edition of F1® 2019 – but that’s not all we’ve got for you today!

✅ Senna vs Prost ✅ Our cover art ✅ F2 confirmed✅ Screenshots

Read everything here: http://bit.ly/F12019-Senna-Prost


“Light Up The Sky”
Performed by The Prodigy
Written by Liam Paul Paris Howlett; Oliver Rhys Burden; Keith Andrew Palmer; Jiri Schelinger
